casebody.data:
Michael E. BOYD, et al., Petitioners,
v.
CALIFORNIA PUBLIC UTILITIES COMMISSION, et al. No. 19-6967 Supreme Court of the United States. Feb. 24, 2020

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until March 16, 2020, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
